ygData.subject: Re: Gnome party
ygData.msgSnippet: If only we could all make lvl 1s and go to PoF to see Cazic! it would be like bixie vs. sand giant! it would be cool to have a plain old gnomey party, gnomes
ygData.messageBody:
If only we could all make lvl 1s and go to PoF to see Cazic! it would be like
bixie vs. sand giant! it would be cool to have a plain old gnomey party,
gnomes taking out Meldrath, the nercomancer guild, the hero, Feddi the mad,
and every thing else in between! how about a pie eating contest too? get a
gnome baker and see which gnome can eat the most in 10 minutes? HURRAY FOR
GNOMES! I like the multi server idea, changing every month or so. how about a
Oasis take-over for one server? this would be real cool. In the words of
Tinik, there's no place like gnome!
